##Xi Jinping's "how to do it" and "why" on international cooperation in fighting the epidemic

Wechat, chinanewsweekly

Function introduction, here is "China News weekly" the head of the weekly gentleman, the influence has the influence you. Come with me to break through the fog, to find the truth, to watch the Times.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
As the number of new crown pneumonia in many countries continues to climb, the global war epidemic has entered a critical moment, "a global chess game, all countries advance and retreat" has increasingly become an international consensus.

"We will actively carry out international cooperation in fighting the epidemic" and "safeguard regional and global public health security. " This is more than a month since China's top leader, Xi Jinping, led China in all-out efforts to combat the epidemic, high-frequency expressions used in intensive "conversations" with the world. These expressions take on unusual significance at a time of global emergency.

International Cooperation in fighting the epidemic is an extremely ambitious concept in itself, but if we return to Xi Jinping's public statements and combine them with China's series of "outward-looking" actions, the connotation of "anti-epidemic International Cooperation"  How to do it, why to make it clear and concrete, and the ancient Chinese wisdom of "Qi" , "Shu" , "FA" and "Dao" become the best footnotes.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
On March 2, Shanghai donated 500,000 masks from Taegu and Gyeongbuk regions of South Korea to Seoul.

"instrument" level, the war epidemic process in China and the world has always been in the material exchange. Pakistan offers masks from its national stockpile to China, and Mongolia donates 30,000 sheep to China... China has received goodwill and help from the world, and Xi has repeatedly thanked relevant countries. As overseas outbreaks have escalated, Mr. Xi has spoken more and more about "providing assistance within our capacity to other countries and regions where the epidemic has spread. ".

Having experienced such difficulties as "shortage of face masks" and "lack of supply of testing reagents" in the initial stage of prevention and control, China shares the same feelings and is particularly aware of the "first demand" of countries with outbreaks, especially those with unstable health systems. In recent days, China has made emergency donations of medical supplies to Pakistan, Japan, South Korea, Iran, the African Union and other countries and organizations within its reach. The Chinese government has also donated $20 million to the WHO to support World Health Organization's international cooperation in the fight against the new pneumonia. The solidarity between nations, the exchange of goods and services, and the emotional solidarity shown are the simplest steps in international cooperation at a time of crisis.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
On March 2, President Xi Jinping of the General Secretary of the Communist Party of China, China's president, and President Central Military Commission of the People's Republic of China visited Beijing to inspect the scientific research work on the prevention and control of NCP. This was Xi's visit to the major epidemic emergency prevention and Control Drug Research Department of the Military Medical Research Institute to learn about the development of vaccines and antibodies. Photo by Ding Haitao, Xinhua news agency

From the beginning of the outbreak, China has strengthened scientific cooperation and data sharing with the world. The prevention and treatment of infectious diseases is a global problem that needs to be solved by the combined efforts of human intelligence. When talking about scientific and technological cooperation in Fighting Epidemic Diseases, Xi Jinping specifically pointed out that, we should strengthen scientific research cooperation with relevant countries, especially those with high incidence of the epidemic, in the areas of traceability, drugs, vaccines and testing, share scientific research data and information, and jointly study and propose countermeasures.

Since the outbreak, china's timely notification of the epidemic situation, sharing of the full genome sequence of some strains of the virus, technical cooperation within the framework of WHO, and sharing with the world of the prevention, control and treatment of the epidemic plan and other technical documents all reflect the proper attitude of a responsible major country. In the age of globalization, the fate of mankind is closely linked. In the face of an epidemic that no country is immune from, greater scientific cooperation between countries and the joint efforts of scientists to combat the epidemic will not only accelerate the pace of the human fight against the virus, but also contribute to a more open and transparent environment, eliminate "information epidemic situation" and create clear public opinion space for global joint anti-epidemic.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
People line up to buy face masks outside a supermarket in Seoul's joongno district on March 1, local time. China News Service reporter, Zeng Nai

"Law" level, in the prevention and control of the epidemic, China is also committed to work with other countries to build a global public health and safety prevention and control system. In his "dialogue" with several foreign leaders, Mr. Xi said China was "responsible for the safety and health of its own people as well as for global public health. ". This shows that China is not only concerned about working together to solve immediate problems, but also committed to promoting institutional cooperation and building a global public health and safety prevention and control system.

For example, "the international community is expected to strengthen coordination and work together to safeguard human health and well-being, " "communicate closely with relevant countries, share experience in epidemic prevention and coordinate prevention and control measures, " This reflects Xi's expectation that countries will further enhance their "tacit agreement" in policy coordination. For example, to promote the establishment of regional and even the global level of the "new contract. ". "We will accelerate the implementation of the Health Action Plan of the Forum on ChinaAfrica Cooperation Beijing summit, promote the construction of the African Center for Disease Control and Prevention, and strengthen china-africa cooperation in public health and disease prevention and control, " Xi said, china has proposed to establish a public health emergency liaison mechanism in China -- ASEAN... the establishment and perfection of these mechanisms will further support the global public health security umbrella for mankind.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
INFOGRAPHIC: On 11 February 2020, the World Health organization-led Global Forum on Innovation in research opened in Geneva with the aim of agreeing a new coronavirus research road map, on the same day, who also announced that the English name of the disease caused by the new coronavirus would be "COVID-19" . China News Service, photo by Deyongjian

"I have always said that mankind is a community of destiny, and that solidarity is the most powerful weapon in the fight against an epidemic that threatens the safety of all peoples" -- if these three dimensions spell out "how to do the right thing" , so the "community of shared future for mankind" that Xi has repeatedly stressed explains "what is the right thing" to the outside world from the height of "Tao" . That was the driving force behind who's assessment that China's leaders had "sufficient leadership and political will" to face the pandemic, The observer stressed.

Whether it is the western wisdom that "no man is an island" , the ancient Persian saying that "all descendants of Adam are brothers, and brothers are like brothers" , or the ancient Chinese saying that "mountains and rivers are foreign, the Sun and the moon are the same" , all of them show the common understanding of different civilizations on Mutual Assistance, fate and common ground. According to the analysis, this is precisely the cognitive basis and operational guidance of Xi's statement that public health security is a common challenge facing mankind and requires countries to work together to address it.

Source: China News Service
